author: kmalhi
msg: A tool to create Validation Key audit report. This tool generates reports in two formats, one is text format and the other is Confluence wiki markup. You can run this tool after you have written some validation tests and it will show you a detailed test coverage report. You can then copy the confluence markup and update the wiki page at https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/OPENEJB/Validation+Keys+Audit+Report
